form.current-chamber: IN THE SENATE OF THE UNITED STATES
form.official-title: Appointing the day for the convening of the second session of the One Hundred Fourteenth Congress.

section.text: That the second regular session of the One Hundred Fourteenth Congress shall begin at noon on Monday, January 4, 2016.

attestation-group.attestation-date: Passed the House of Representatives December 15, 2015.
